yingyinNormal.en: Dr. Slaughter, MD? Actually, millionaire weapons designer, Malcolm Chastletick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 屠杀博士? 他是身价百万的武器设计师，马尔科姆· 查瑟蒂克。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm a hat designer, so I go to Malaysia and Sri Lanka a lot for materials.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是个帽子设计师，我常会去马来西亚以及斯里兰卡去弄材料。

yingyinNormal.en: Lily white. In your designer heels and tailored dresses, I mean, look at this property, Mrs. Underwood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 白得彻头彻尾，穿着设计师鞋，量体剪裁的衣服，看看这片地产，安德伍德夫人。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, I mean I would give anything to work for a designer, you know, or a buyer. I just don't want to be 30 and still work here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，我愿意不计一切，为设计师或采购人工作，我不想到了30岁还在这里工作。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know, I thought she did. She knew he was a fashion designer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，我以为她知道，她知道他是位时装设计师。

yingyinNormal.en: Comments about being hot, questions about bra size, these are compliments? From a gay fashion designer, they are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 说她性感问她胸围 你称这些为恭维话吗？出自一位同性恋时装设计师之口，是的。

yingyinNormal.en: This is GHB. This is what I made. I call it "Snowball Chi", it's a designer drug.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是G水，这是我做的，我叫它「芝加哥雪球」，是种化合致幻药。

yingyinNormal.en: That you just missed the gelato and designer coffee cart. Espresso hazelnut praline?
yingyinNormal.zh: 是你们错过了冰淇淋跟好咖啡的推车啦，要咖啡果仁夹心冰淇淋吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh Monica, listen, I saw down at the hardware store, they got those designer tiles on sale, if you ever want to redo the bathroom floor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对了，我在装潢建材店,看到名牌瓷砖在特价,你可以重铺浴室地板。

yingyinNormal.en: The point is nobody expected us to be able to actually run Dad's company. But with Evelyn as designer, and myself as operator, we threw ourselves into building DevTech into what it is today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 关键在于没人以为我们能撑得起爸爸的公司。但有伊芙琳负责设计，我负责运营我们全身心投入到公司中去造就了现在的德福公司。
